tool_description: Use this api for short url decoding and find the original url without going though the url
title: Short Url Deocder

api_list.name: Get Proxies
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://short-url-deocder.p.rapidapi.com/api/proxy"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "short-url-deocder.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
